publisher			Frozenbyte							
publish_time	 2007年11月14日		
desc_long							评测						"I greatly enjoyed the unending masses of aliens which I splattered all over the landscape with pistol, machine gun, and flame thrower."- GamersWanted - 92% (full review)"[The] developers decided to "remix" this game and release a hybrid expansion/follow-up. The result is Shadowgrounds Survivor, and it's every bit as good as the first release. Survivor, the extended remix of Shadowgrounds, is a must-have for any fans of action-horror."- Worthplaying - 89% (full review)"FrozenByte definitely has a winner on its hand. If you have the hankering to play an action top down shooter that looks good and has addictive gameplay, look no further than Shadowgrounds: Survivor."- GamingTrend - 89% (full review)"I don't know of any other top-down shooters for the PC which are done as well, or look as good or cost $20.  You also receive the tools to completely mod the game and create additional maps.  Generally my rule is that if I feel like replaying a game right after I finish it, that's a good enough indication of its worth, and Survivor is definitely worth it."- 2024 - 85% (full review)												关于这款游戏							生存只是这个游戏的一部分。屡获殊荣的游戏 阴影地带 带来了全新的篇章！阴影地带 幸存者 讲述了人类最后的幸存者在木卫三上遭遇外星人猛烈攻击的故事！三个角色 全新的战术升级系统 包括武器和角色，例如特殊攻击强力火焰和威武的暴力杀手。任务模式 强化了 阴影地带 的剧情，将故事拓展到新的环境里，包括雪地和冰川，废弃的货物通道，以及新亚特兰提斯殖民地。生存模式 尽可能多的消灭外星人。选择一个适合你的角色把外星人打回外太空！编辑工具 允许玩家积极参与 阴影地带 的自制用户社区 - 或者是享受成果！AGEIA PhysX 通过模拟成百上千碎片的物理特性，将爆炸效果提升到一个新的台阶！新的游戏特征 例如岗哨炮塔和机甲！新的视觉效果 包括肆虐的暴风雪效果，新的武器效果以及更多！						
